data.description: Spectacular move-in ready home in Covington with over 5500+ square feet 6 Bedrooms/ 4 Baths plus  A full finish basement with a bedroom and 2 additional flex rooms, great for in law suite, formal living room, formal dining room, family room, and HUGE master bedroom with SITTING AREA. The kitchen includes pantry, breakfast bar. Outside accent lighting to front of the home. If you are looking for a statement home, this is one that you must see. The master bath includes a double vanity soaking tub, and large glass shower, along with a very spacious two walk-in closets. Everything about this house makes it one you'll need to view to appreciate.
